# API conventions (routes and services)

Project hub: repository root `AGENTS.md`.

# API Code Organization Standards

## File Naming Conventions

### Routes
- `routes/subdomain_assets.py` - Subdomain asset endpoints
- `routes/ip_assets.py` - IP asset endpoints
- `routes/url_assets.py` - URL asset endpoints
- `routes/nuclei_findings.py` - Nuclei findings endpoints
- `routes/typosquat_findings.py` - Typosquat findings endpoints
- `routes/<entity>.py` - Generic entity endpoints (programs, workflows, auth)

### Repositories
- `repository/subdomain_assets_repo.py` - Subdomain repository
- `repository/ip_assets_repo.py` - IP repository
- `repository/nuclei_findings_repo.py` - Nuclei findings repository
- `repository/program_repo.py` - Program repository
- `repository/batch_repository.py` - Batch operations repository

### Services
- `services/unified_asset_processor.py` - Unified asset processing
- `services/unified_findings_processor.py` - Unified findings processing
- `services/event_publisher.py` - NATS event publisher
- `services/hackerone_service.py` - HackerOne integration
- `services/internal_token_service.py` - Internal token management

### Models
- `models/postgres.py` - SQLAlchemy ORM models
- `models/user_postgres.py` - User Pydantic models
- `models/<entity>.py` - Entity-specific Pydantic models

